            <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 list-disc list-inside">
              <li>Provide accurate, current, and complete information</li>
              <li>Maintain and update your information to keep it accurate</li>
              <li>Maintain the security of your password and account</li>
              <li>Accept responsibility for all activities under your account</li>
              <li>Notify us immediately of any unauthorized use of your account</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <!-- Orders and Payment -->
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">5. Orders and Payment</h2>
            
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-6">Order Acceptance</h3>
